des: 96 K-T-O is Redding's True Oldies Station. We proudly play America's favorite music from the 60's and 70's. We're an affiliate of Scott Shannon's True Oldies Channel. We supplement the network presentation with local Shasta County community information including News, Sports, and Weather. We also conduct contests and promote events.
